## `test_fuse_create_write_read(mount)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-fbasic-2 -->
<!-- trace: skipped -->
<!-- trace_skip_reason: syscall boundary -->

### Postconditions

```python
path = mount / "hello.txt"
with open(path, "wb") as f:
    f.write(b"hello fuse")

with open(path, "rb") as f:
    assert f.read() == b"hello fuse"
```

