## `test_fuse_mkdir_readdir(mount)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-fbasic-3 -->
<!-- trace: skipped -->
<!-- trace_skip_reason: syscall boundary -->

### Postconditions

```python
(mount / "a").mkdir()
(mount / "b").mkdir()
(mount / "a" / "inner").mkdir()

names_root = sorted(os.listdir(mount))
assert names_root == ["a", "b"]

names_a = os.listdir(mount / "a")
assert names_a == ["inner"]
```

