## `test_fuse_stat(mount)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-fbasic-4 -->
<!-- trace: skipped -->
<!-- trace_skip_reason: syscall boundary -->

### Postconditions

```python
path = mount / "f"
with open(path, "wb") as f:
    f.write(b"x" * 1234)

st = os.stat(path)
