## `test_fuse_rename(mount)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-fbasic-6 -->
<!-- trace: skipped -->
<!-- trace_skip_reason: syscall boundary -->

### Postconditions

```python
src = mount / "src"
dst = mount / "dst"
src.write_bytes(b"content")

os.rename(src, dst)
assert not src.exists()
assert dst.read_bytes() == b"content"
```

