## `test_fuse_write_past_eof_zero_pad(mount)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-fbasic-8 -->
<!-- trace: skipped -->
<!-- trace_skip_reason: syscall boundary -->

### Postconditions

```python
path = mount / "f"
with open(path, "wb") as f:
    f.seek(100)
    f.write(b"end")

with open(path, "rb") as f:
    data = f.read()
assert data == b"\x00" * 100 + b"end"
assert len(data) == 103
```

